      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61564860.pdf_81_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "飞的形式还有“飞”。它是指在原有棋呈“”字 形的对角线交点处行棋。",
        "bbox": [
          0.14347539626158953,
          0.5331252929040727,
          0.8514441548638592,
          0.5883882805831534
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61564860.pdf_81_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "图2-118白△就叫白棋原有一子的大飞。同样，假若白方 今后在A、B、C、D、E、F、G任何一处行棋，都叫大飞。",
        "bbox": [
          0.14582745193800903,
